    "• f R ∪ T ∪ {i} -f (R ∪ T).",
    "(10)Currently, Owen value has not been widely applied in feature attribution research for ML models.",
    "However, Owen value holds great potential and is expected to be employed in various domains of ML models.",
    "For instance, it can be leveraged to explain ML-based automatic driving decision models.",
    "This is particularly relevant due to the collective nature of traffic vehicles, which naturally forms a priority coalition."
